enemies.name: The Stuff of Nightmares
enemies.note: The Stuff of Nightmares is a sentient black hole that feeds on memories. It's taken the shape of a human after absorbing so many human memories. It cries because of all the memories it has to erase, but is happy because some are better off without certain memories. It seems to have been branded by an organization. Made by StarmanDX
